text: Maui resident Lauraine Ayers-Briel filed a sexual assault complaint against a local physician. But nearly a year later, she is wondering what happened to her allegations — and why the physician she named is still practicing.
author: ahofschneider

text: “Our whole response to global warming is a bit baffling to me. It’s as close to an existential crisis as we’re likely to see, absent a nuclear exchange, and it just doesn’t feel like we’re taking it very serious.”
author: ahofschneider
